        since M ≥ q_j ℓ_j* A_j ℓ_j and e_i is eigenvector with eigenvalue λ_i

     4. Combining: det(A_j) ≤ (d/α_j²)^{|I_j|} × (1/q_j)^{|I_j|} × ∏_{i∈I_j} λ_i

     5. Taking q_j power and product: ∏_j det(A_j)^{q_j} ≤ d^{Ac} × ℰ(D)² × (∏_j α_j^{-2q_j m_j}) × ∏_j (∏_{i∈I_j} λ_i)^{q_j}

