  /- (by claude) Step 30: Construct the chain of inequalities using established bounds.

     The mathematical argument is:
     1. By Hadamard (via greedy construction):
        det(A_j) ≤ (d/α_j²)^{m_j} × q_j^{-m_j} × ∏_{i∈I_j} λ_i

